      "content": "I hear you saying you're worried about being a liability, but management's priority right now is reducing operational overhead. If the template system meets the basic requirements for customer satisfaction, the company is going to proceed with the change regardless. Can you explain, in practical terms, what specific failures you think will happen when customers start getting those canned template responses instead of your current level of service?",
